OL,5, An "unscheduled" safeguarding audit and
OL,6, review has been launched in the        
OL,7, Catholic church.                       
OL,9,FThe Catholic Safeguarding Standards    
OL,10,FAgency will carry out the review into  
OL,11,Fthe Diocese of Hexham and Newcastle.   
OL,13,FThe BBC understands it involves claims 
OL,14,Ffrom a whistleblower that men were     
OL,15,Fregularly drinking on the St Mary's    
OL,16,FCathedral complex during lockdown 2021.
OL,18,FThe inquiry is also expected to examine
OL,19,Fthe circumstances into the suicide of  
OL,20,Fthe Canon Michael McCoy.               
